      "value": {
        "latex": "Développer en série de Fourier la fonction : $x  \\mapsto |\\sin x|$.",
        "html": "<p>Développer en série de Fourier la fonction : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x  \\mapsto |\\sin x|\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "35cb08da-e650-4990-a9c8-1dddcda10462",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Application : Soit $f : {[a,b]} \\to \\R$ continue.\n    Montrer que $ \\int_{t=a}^b f(t)|\\sin nt|\\,d t \\to\n    \\frac2\\pi \\int_{t=a}^b f(t)\\,d t$ lorsque $n\\to\\infty$.",
        "html": "<p>Application : Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f : {[a,b]} \\to \\R\\)</span> continue. Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\int_{t=a}^b f(t)|\\sin nt|\\,d t \\to\n    \\frac2\\pi \\int_{t=a}^b f(t)\\,d t\\)</span> lorsque <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\to\\infty\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5d813f77-0ff6-4127-af97-2284bf2f6ad6",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$|\\sin x| = \\frac2\\pi -\\frac 4\\pi\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty\n             \\frac{\\cos 2nx}{4n^2-1}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(|\\sin x| = \\frac2\\pi -\\frac 4\\pi\\sum_{n=1}^\\infty\n             \\frac{\\cos 2nx}{4n^2-1}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ],
